 those bombs or you'll run out of lives!\n\n## ABOUT\n- Compete in over 90 minigames.\n- Easy, medium, and hard mode.\n- Local, global, and friends leaderboards.\n- Tuned for all experience and comfort levels.\n\n## DESCRIPTION\n- Arcade-style target shooting minigames.\n- Hardcore mode, for experienced players to challenge themselves and the leaderboards.\n- Newcomer mode, low intensity to ease in new players.\n- Relive that retro arcade light-gun experience, in VR!", "short_description": "On Point is a shooter, filled with Warioware-style arcade minigames. Think, aim, and blast your way to a high score through endless shooting minigames, but don't hit those bombs or you'll run out of lives!"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://onpoint.game/privacy.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://onpoint.game/eula.html", "publisher_name": "Actuator Games", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://onpoint.game/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "3744040075834813"}, {"id": "1592192974313489"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "8942897762423518"}, "review_messages": [""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent-lga3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974458_849625540664188_6381539603823533787_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=hd4QltjMgTAQ7kNvgHIEl9J&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-lga3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDTXC8S5WtLD